(2929, 'Colostop 30 capsules', 'كولوستوب 30 كبسول', '', '20', 'Peppermint oil+dill oil+fennel oil+anise oil', 'Sigma > macro group pharmaceuticals', 'Capsule', 'كبسولة', '', 'Git disturbances', '', 'Indicated for the over-the-counter use for:
